## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let loadImg = (src)=>{
		return new Promise((resolve,reject)=>{
        	let image = new Image();
          image.onload = function(){
          		resolve(image)
          };
          image.onerror = function(){
              reject(new Error('Could not image au' + src));
          }
          image.src = src;
        })
	}
